headline: Baker Hughes Secures Subsea Contract for Sakarya Gas Field
summary: Baker Hughes bagged a Turkish contract to supply subsea production and intelligent completion systems for the strategic Sakarya Gas Field Phase 3 project.

headline: Is There Now an Opportunity in Baker Hughes After 39.9% Share Price Rise?
summary: If you have been eyeing Baker Hughes recently, you are not alone. With the energy sector heating up and global demand trends keeping investors on their toes, Baker Hughes shares have quietly outperformed. Over the last year, the stock has gained a remarkable 39.9%, and that momentum is even more impressive when you look further back: 271.2% over five years speaks volumes about how far the company has come. Just last week, the price ticked up another 1.9%, building on solid gains of 8.6% over...
